This directory contains design specifications and prompt-composition patterns
vendored from nexu-io/open-design (https://github.com/nexu-io/open-design),
Copyright 2026 Open Design contributors, licensed under the Apache License,
Version 2.0. The full license text lives in /licenses/LICENSE-APACHE-2.0.

Each vendored file also carries its own attribution block (either as Markdown
frontmatter `source:` keys for SKILL.md / DESIGN.md files, or as a top-of-file
comment for TypeScript ports).

