--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Ported patterns
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ai/compose-system-prompt.ts
   Ported from apps/daemon/src/prompts/system.ts in nexu-io/open-design.
   Layered concatenation pattern with `\n\n---\n\n` separators and
   composeSystemPrompt() function shape. CVeetje-specific layer set;
   the stack ordering and separator convention are preserved.

recipes/_visual-directions/{editorial-monocle,modern-minimal,tech-utility,brutalist,soft-warm}.ts
   The 5 baseline visual directions from open-design's web app, ported to
   TypeScript constants with OKLch palette tokens and Google Fonts font stacks.
   Original color values and font choices preserved; only the data shape
   (Markdown → TS constant) is changed.
